1
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:34,920
Your sister's off to the capital.

2
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:37,200
It's not like Tongzhou.

3
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:39,040
So you take good care of her, all right?

4
00:01:39,239 --> 00:01:40,319
Don't worry, Grandma.

5
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:44,680
You're very kind, Mother.

6
00:01:45,359 --> 00:01:46,519
I'm humbled.

7
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:51,239
I know life isn't easy for you.

8
00:01:51,599 --> 00:01:53,040
Just

9
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:55,560
take care of yourself.

10
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,359
That's the greatest gift

11
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,959
you could ever give me.

12
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:07,079
I've heard what you've been through

13
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:09,280
these past few months in the capital.

14
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:11,560
You're a smart girl.

15
00:02:12,159 --> 00:02:13,520
But remember this.

16
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:14,919
No matter how hard things get

17
00:02:14,919 --> 00:02:16,960
from now on,

18
00:02:17,319 --> 00:02:18,919
don't ever carry it all alone.

19
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:21,479
You just let me know.

20
00:02:22,319 --> 00:02:23,479
I will, Grandmother.

21
00:02:30,599 --> 00:02:31,599
Mother.

22
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:42,120
That Mrs. Ji is finally gone.

23
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,000
Yesterday,
all I wanted was a little piece of that pinkish gauze

24
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:44,919
for a trim.

25
00:02:45,319 --> 00:02:46,759
The mistress hadn't even said a word,

26
00:02:46,919 --> 00:02:48,400
and she gave me a dirty look instead.

27
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:49,840
She starts going on about how cold it is
and why would anyone use gauze.

28
00:02:50,919 --> 00:02:52,759
Then she says I don't know the value of anything.

29
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,120
Pfft!

30
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,719
An outsider,
coming into our Gu manor

31
00:02:57,479 --> 00:02:58,439
and telling everyone what to do.

32
00:02:58,919 --> 00:03:00,000
Unbelievable.

33
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:01,800
Mother,

34
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,199
please don't cross Mrs. Ji.

35
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:06,280
She's even tougher than the mistress.

36
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,960
And honestly, the fabric thing is secondary.

37
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,120
My coming-of-age ceremony next year
is what really matters.

38
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,840
Have you asked the mistress

39
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:15,000
how much silver the palace will give?

40
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:16,879
Well.

41
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,400
My lady asked.

42
00:03:18,879 --> 00:03:20,599
The mistress says by the rules,

43
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,360
the palace can only give two hundred taels.

44
00:03:22,719 --> 00:03:23,879
She'll add another hundred

45
00:03:23,879 --> 00:03:25,120
from her private purse.

46
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,879
So my lady thought

47
00:03:27,039 --> 00:03:28,439
we add seven hundred ourselves,

48
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,639
and make it a thousand.

49
00:03:30,919 --> 00:03:32,319
We can't do that.

50
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:33,680
You worked so hard

51
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,719
to save that money.

52
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:36,039
We can't just throw it away.

53
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,520
Besides,
that would only

54
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,800
be a thousand taels.

55
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,080
But I heard that
for my eldest sister's coming-of-age ceremony,

56
00:03:41,879 --> 00:03:42,800
they spent over ten thousand.

57
00:03:43,039 --> 00:03:43,840
Lan,

58
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,080
her coming-of-age ceremony

59
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,439
was all paid for

60
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:47,800
by the Ji family.

61
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:49,879
We didn't spend a single tael.

62
00:03:55,439 --> 00:03:57,280
Just because my mother's family isn't powerful,

63
00:03:57,439 --> 00:03:59,000
I'm supposed to keep my head down.

64
00:04:00,199 --> 00:04:01,479
I'm a concubine's daughter as it is.

65
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,599
If my coming-of-age ceremony

66
00:04:02,599 --> 00:04:03,680
is too shabby,

67
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,639
people will only look down on me even more.

68
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,439
And when it's time to find a match,

69
00:04:06,439 --> 00:04:07,960
what kind of good family would want me?

70
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:11,000
But honestly, my mother's family isn't bad at all.

71
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:13,000
A fourth-rank official in the Court of Imperial Sacrifices.

72
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,319
Even if he's retired,

73
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,040
that's still way better than the Ji family,

74
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:17,120
who are just merchants.

75
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:19,560
I don't understand what my mother was thinking.

76
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:20,959
Just for the sake of Father,

77
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,639
she abandoned her own parents

78
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:24,399
and married him as a secondary wife.

79
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,399
Miss.

80
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,279
Here's a letter from our young lord.

81
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,879
Could you give it to Miss Gu?

82
00:04:32,959 --> 00:04:33,639
Thank you.

83
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,079
Sure.

84
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,079
Changshun.

85
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:46,839
Second Miss.

86
00:04:47,439 --> 00:04:48,319
That man just now

87
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:49,920
was from the Marquis of Changxing's residence, wasn't he?

88
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:51,720
Miss Ziling, sharp eyes.

89
00:04:51,839 --> 00:04:53,199
Yes, he's from there.

90
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,040
He came

91
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,600
to deliver an invitation to the eldest Miss.

92
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,040
Just as well.

93
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,800
I'm heading to the main house

94
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,759
to find her for dinner.

95
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,160
I'll give it to her for you.

96
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:09,480
There's only you at the gate.

97
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,600
You can't leave your post.

98
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:16,720
Fair enough.

99
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:18,399
Thank you very much, Second Miss.

100
00:05:37,399 --> 00:05:39,199
[Thank you for saving me outside Baoxiang Temple.]

101
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,720
[Tomorrow between 9 and 11 AM,

102
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,800
I will host a banquet at Linxia.]

103
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,199
[I await your arrival.]

104
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:46,519
[I knew it.]

105
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:47,600
[There's something between the young lord and my eldest sister.]

106
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,040
This one seems thicker.

107
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:51,480
Yeah, and the color is nicer too.

108
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:56,079
Madam.

109
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,879
You wanted to see me?

110
00:05:59,399 --> 00:06:00,240
Yes, come sit down.

111
00:06:01,759 --> 00:06:02,879
I made a few pairs of

112
00:06:02,879 --> 00:06:04,079
knee pads,

113
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,720
all stuffed with goose down.

114
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,639
This pair is for Yao.

115
00:06:07,879 --> 00:06:08,600
And

116
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,959
this one is for Rong.

117
00:06:10,319 --> 00:06:11,839
He's almost back,

118
00:06:11,839 --> 00:06:12,800
isn't he?

119
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,079
And this pair

120
00:06:15,639 --> 00:06:16,839
is for your father.

121
00:06:18,639 --> 00:06:19,800
I've already prepared a calligraphy scroll

122
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,360
for Rong

123
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:23,319
as a welcoming gift.

124
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,759
You don't need to go out of your way

125
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:26,240
to prepare anything in my name.

126
00:06:27,519 --> 00:06:28,839
As for Father,

127
00:06:29,199 --> 00:06:30,160
if you want to give him something, just do it.

128
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,920
You don't have to say it's from me.

129
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,839
I understand how you feel.

130
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:38,399
But

131
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,279
Rong is your own brother.

132
00:06:40,639 --> 00:06:42,040
You didn't grow up together,

133
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:43,439
so it's easy to be distant.

134
00:06:43,759 --> 00:06:45,759
Antiques and calligraphy

135
00:06:46,199 --> 00:06:47,120
are nice,

136
00:06:47,319 --> 00:06:48,120
but they're also

137
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,560
a bit cold.

138
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,920
Something made by hand

139
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,079
carries more heart.

140
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,199
Right?

141
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:56,639
As for your father,

142
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,240
he may have his faults,

143
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:01,040
but he's your own flesh and blood.

144
00:07:01,639 --> 00:07:02,879
If word gets out that you've been cold toward him,

145
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,759
people will only blame you.

146
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,000
And besides,

147
00:07:07,439 --> 00:07:08,920
Your marriage can't wait any longer.

148
00:07:09,279 --> 00:07:10,759
He is an official,

149
00:07:10,759 --> 00:07:12,040
and knows a lot of people.

150
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,800
If he would just help a little,

151
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:17,000
finding a good match would be much easier.

152
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,879
[Marriage talk again.]

153
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:20,920
[And the mistress still thinks

154
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,160
he can be counted on.]

155
00:07:23,439 --> 00:07:25,360
Yao has just started at Cunshan Academy.

156
00:07:25,439 --> 00:07:26,839
I wonder how he's doing.

157
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,480
Since the knee pads are already made,

158
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:29,639
I should send them to him

159
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:30,920
as soon as possible.

160
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,439
Maybe I'll go to the academy

161
00:07:32,439 --> 00:07:33,560
tomorrow.

162
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:34,959
Sounds good.

163
00:07:45,839 --> 00:07:46,800
This crossbow is nicely done.

164
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,120
Give him ten taels.
Yes, sir.

165
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,240
Thank you, my lord.

166
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,120
If you can extend the range

167
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,680
another fifty paces,

168
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,800
I'll give you a hundred.

169
00:08:00,639 --> 00:08:02,560
I'll get right on it, my lord.

170
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:08,800
My lord,

171
00:08:09,199 --> 00:08:11,199
we're supposed to meet Miss Gu at nine.

172
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:13,319
Shouldn't we go?

173
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,399
What's the rush?

174
00:08:15,079 --> 00:08:16,079
Let her wait.

175
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:19,079
Yes, my lord.

176
00:08:23,519 --> 00:08:24,279
Fine.

177
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,480
Look at you, so impatient.

178
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:27,480
Let's go.

179
00:08:36,879 --> 00:08:38,639
It's already an hour past the time.

180
00:08:39,399 --> 00:08:40,440
Why isn't she here yet?

181
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,240
Maybe

182
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,519
she got held up on the way.

183
00:08:43,759 --> 00:08:44,840
It's not far anyway.

184
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,240
Send someone

185
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:47,559
to the Gu household to meet her.

186
00:08:47,919 --> 00:08:48,639
Yes, sir.

187
00:09:07,399 --> 00:09:07,919
Miss.

188
00:09:08,279 --> 00:09:09,519
I told Luo Gui'er not to wait.

189
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:10,840
He should find a place out of the wind

190
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:11,879
and come back in an hour
to pick you up.

191
00:09:18,799 --> 00:09:20,320
Our young lady is Miss Gu.

192
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:22,720
She's here to see Mr. Chen Xuanqing.

193
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,240
Would you mind letting him know, sir?

194
00:09:24,519 --> 00:09:26,159
Please follow me inside.

195
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:41,519
My lord.

196
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:42,720
What happened?

197
00:09:43,039 --> 00:09:43,799
Where's Gu Jinzhao?

198
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,120
Miss Gu,

199
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,360
she went to the academy.

200
00:09:54,679 --> 00:09:56,279
The academy again.

201
00:10:00,799 --> 00:10:01,480
Top Scholar.

202
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,840
A Miss Gu is outside

203
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:04,559
asking for you.

204
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:05,759
Miss Gu?

205
00:10:06,039 --> 00:10:06,840
The one

206
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:08,320
who was here with Ms. Ji last time.

207
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:11,759
Are you sure she wants to see him?

208
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:12,559
Not me?

209
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:14,519
She didn't mention you, sir.

210
00:10:14,919 --> 00:10:16,159
Got it.

211
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:25,879
The other day, your grandmother and Miss Gu

212
00:10:25,879 --> 00:10:26,720
came to my house.

213
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,799
I lent her a book.

214
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:31,440
She's probably here to return it.

215
00:10:33,799 --> 00:10:34,799
But I just remembered

216
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,360
the lecturer needs to see me.

217
00:10:36,519 --> 00:10:37,720
He told me to wait for him.

218
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:39,120
I really can't leave.

219
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,399
So
maybe you could help me out?

220
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,159
Go see Miss Gu

221
00:10:42,399 --> 00:10:43,679
and get the book back for me.

222
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:44,519
Would you?

223
00:10:44,759 --> 00:10:45,840
I can't go to her.

224
00:10:47,399 --> 00:10:48,519
You know my cousin's temper.

225
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,360
Since she didn't ask for me,

226
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:52,279
if I showed up,

227
00:10:52,759 --> 00:10:53,840
she'd be furious.

228
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:57,360
So here's what we do.

229
00:10:57,799 --> 00:10:59,480
Send someone else

230
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,519
to see her.

231
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,000
Tell her you got held up

232
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,279
by the lecturer

233
00:11:03,639 --> 00:11:04,639
and can't come.

234
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,159
Then have her give the book

235
00:11:06,159 --> 00:11:07,360
to that person

236
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,080
to bring back.
What do you think?

237
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:10,519
Sounds good.

238
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,080
Miss.

239
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:38,879
Miss Gu.

240
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,600
Mr. Zhang.

241
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:44,159
Long time no see

242
00:11:44,399 --> 00:11:45,600
since the Chen house.

243
00:11:45,919 --> 00:11:46,559
Anyway,

244
00:11:46,759 --> 00:11:48,000
Xuruo got called away by the lecturer,

245
00:11:48,159 --> 00:11:49,360
won't be back for a while.

246
00:11:49,679 --> 00:11:50,559
He said

247
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:52,240
you have a book for him.

248
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:54,159
You can just hand it to me.

249
00:11:55,279 --> 00:11:57,440
So he sent you to pick it up?

250
00:11:57,519 --> 00:11:58,240
That's right.

251
00:12:01,639 --> 00:12:02,960
One moment, please.

252
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,120
Much obliged.

253
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,159
My pleasure.

254
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:30,240
Well, well. A touching scene of young love.

255
00:12:36,519 --> 00:12:38,039
I thought you were so busy.

256
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:40,519
Turns out you're here meeting some other man.

257
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:41,919
Greetings, my lord.

258
00:12:42,159 --> 00:12:43,120
I think you've misunderstood.

259
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,399
I was just...

260
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,440
Are you following me?

261
00:12:52,519 --> 00:12:53,120
Don't
flatter yourself.

262
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,000
I just happened

263
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,320
to pass by

264
00:12:56,639 --> 00:12:57,279
and saw you here,
messing around with a man.

265
00:12:58,519 --> 00:12:59,440
That's all.

266
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:02,840
So this is the one you've set your sights on?

267
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,200
Nonsense.

268
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,360
Are you cured now

269
00:13:06,639 --> 00:13:07,919
and looking for a fight again?

270
00:13:08,799 --> 00:13:10,240
You saved me once,

271
00:13:10,559 --> 00:13:11,679
and now you think you can walk all over me.

272
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:12,840
Don't forget,

273
00:13:13,039 --> 00:13:13,960
if it weren't for my help,

274
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:14,600
you'd already be a married woman
in the Liu family.

275
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:16,679
So that's why

276
00:13:16,679 --> 00:13:17,720
you didn't want to marry into the Lius.

277
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:20,080
You went through all that trouble begging for my help.

278
00:13:20,559 --> 00:13:22,080
I thought you had high standards.

279
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:24,120
But after all that,

280
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:25,600
this is the kind of man you're after.

281
00:13:26,919 --> 00:13:27,960
No matter how bad your reputation is,

282
00:13:28,159 --> 00:13:28,720
you don't just settle for

283
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,799
the first thing that comes along.

284
00:13:30,519 --> 00:13:31,559
Who I choose

285
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:33,080
has nothing to do with you, my lord.

286
00:13:33,279 --> 00:13:34,279
But

287
00:13:34,759 --> 00:13:36,159
you are the Crown Prince's companion.

288
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:37,879
Shouldn't you be with His Highness?

289
00:13:37,879 --> 00:13:39,320
Why do you spend your days following me instead?

290
00:13:39,759 --> 00:13:41,000
If you're well enough,

291
00:13:41,279 --> 00:13:42,720
go back to your duties at the palace.

292
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:44,480
If you're still unwell

293
00:13:44,639 --> 00:13:46,240
then go home and rest. Leave me alone.

294
00:13:47,159 --> 00:13:48,879
What's the matter?

295
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:49,960
Upset that I caught you in the act?

296
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:50,919
Boring.

297
00:13:51,399 --> 00:13:52,919
I have things to do. I'll take my leave.

298
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:57,720
What are you doing?

299
00:14:00,519 --> 00:14:01,360
Trying to leave, are you?

300
00:14:03,399 --> 00:14:04,120
Li Xianhuai.

301
00:14:04,679 --> 00:14:05,240
Now,

302
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,399
go look into this man.

303
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,039
I want to see

304
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:10,559
what kind of brilliant scholar

305
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:12,559
has caught

306
00:14:12,559 --> 00:14:13,600
our Miss Gu's eye.

307
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:14,519
Yes.

308
00:14:14,919 --> 00:14:15,720
Wait.

309
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:17,720
My lord, you've misunderstood.

310
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:19,480
There's nothing between Miss Gu and me.

311
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:20,399
Miss Gu,

312
00:14:21,879 --> 00:14:22,600
please
explain to the young lord.

313
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:24,799
Please.

314
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,240
My lord.

315
00:14:27,519 --> 00:14:29,120
Mr. Zhang

316
00:14:29,399 --> 00:14:30,679
has done nothing to you.

317
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:32,080
Why are you investigating him?

318
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:33,240
I'll look into whoever I want.

319
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:34,159
What's it to you?
Li Xianhuai.

320
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:35,440
Yes.
Wait.

321
00:14:37,519 --> 00:14:38,480
If you have a problem,

322
00:14:38,799 --> 00:14:39,679
take it out on me.

323
00:14:39,799 --> 00:14:41,159
Don't bully Mr. Zhang.

324
00:14:41,519 --> 00:14:42,759
He just passed

325
00:14:42,759 --> 00:14:44,080
the provincial exam,

326
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:45,919
and

327
00:14:45,919 --> 00:14:47,000
he can't withstand your scrutiny.

328
00:14:47,559 --> 00:14:48,480
If people find out

329
00:14:48,639 --> 00:14:50,120
he's offended you,

330
00:14:50,279 --> 00:14:51,039
they'll
trample him.

331
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,039
How will

332
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:54,799
he ever take the imperial exams

333
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:57,240
or become an official?

334
00:14:57,759 --> 00:14:59,759
You're worried about his future.

335
00:15:03,679 --> 00:15:04,679
I remember now.

336
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,039
I've seen you

337
00:15:07,039 --> 00:15:07,559
at Chen Yanyun's place.
Yes, yes.

338
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:10,600
I had the honor of meeting you, my lord.

339
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,120
Let me ask you something.

340
00:15:12,519 --> 00:15:14,559
If you gave up the imperial exams

341
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:16,720
and became a staff officer in our marquisate,

342
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:18,879
would you be willing?

343
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:20,159
Don't push it too far.

344
00:15:20,279 --> 00:15:21,600
My lord, are you serious?

345
00:15:23,399 --> 00:15:24,559
What if I am?

346
00:15:29,039 --> 00:15:29,840
Mr. Zhang,

347
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:31,000
what are you doing?

348
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:32,000
Don't tell me

349
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:33,519
you're giving up the spring exams?

350
00:15:34,519 --> 00:15:35,399
Miss Gu.

351
00:15:36,039 --> 00:15:37,679
To be honest, passing the provincial exam

352
00:15:37,919 --> 00:15:39,399
was pure luck.

353
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:40,639
It's all thanks to my ancestors.

354
00:15:40,919 --> 00:15:42,440
I know my own limits.

355
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:43,960
I have no strength left

356
00:15:44,279 --> 00:15:45,120
for the exam path.

357
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:46,440
Even if I sat

358
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:47,639
for the spring exams,

359
00:15:47,799 --> 00:15:49,200
I'd get nowhere.

360
00:15:49,639 --> 00:15:50,879
A fifth rank post

361
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:52,159
in the marquisate.

362
00:15:52,799 --> 00:15:54,039
Why wouldn't I be willing?

363
00:15:54,519 --> 00:15:55,159
Well,

364
00:15:56,440 --> 00:15:58,840
if I could serve you, my lord,

365
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:01,120
I would gladly give up the spring exams

366
00:16:01,399 --> 00:16:03,240
and follow your command.

367
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:13,120
What a shame.

368
00:16:15,759 --> 00:16:17,240
I was just joking.

369
00:16:18,240 --> 00:16:19,279
Why are you taking it so seriously?

370
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,039
You.

371
00:16:21,879 --> 00:16:23,039
How could you do this?

372
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:26,759
How else could I

373
00:16:26,919 --> 00:16:28,279
show you that

374
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:31,039
people don't always act the way you expect?

375
00:16:31,799 --> 00:16:33,159
You said if I investigated him,

376
00:16:33,399 --> 00:16:34,480
I'd ruin his exams

377
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:35,320
and career.

378
00:16:35,799 --> 00:16:36,279
But

379
00:16:36,279 --> 00:16:37,519
this man doesn't even have the confidence

380
00:16:37,519 --> 00:16:38,240
to sit for the spring exams.

381
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,639
I dangled a little bait

382
00:16:40,759 --> 00:16:42,320
and he jumped at it.

383
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:43,919
With that kind of character,

384
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:45,360
even if he became an official,

385
00:16:45,519 --> 00:16:47,480
he'd just be a useless seat warmer.

386
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:48,960
Come to think of it,

387
00:16:49,159 --> 00:16:50,320
I just happened

388
00:16:50,440 --> 00:16:51,679
to uncover a mediocre talent

389
00:16:51,679 --> 00:16:52,440
for the court.

390
00:16:54,240 --> 00:16:55,519
How wonderful.

391
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:56,399
You.

392
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:57,519
You.

393
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:07,240
Oh no!

394
00:17:08,519 --> 00:17:09,240
What is it?
What happened?

395
00:17:10,079 --> 00:17:11,559
Mr. Zhang got into a fight

396
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:12,839
and coughed up blood.

397
00:17:13,079 --> 00:17:14,480
He's been taken to a clinic.

398
00:17:15,799 --> 00:17:16,640
What?

399
00:17:20,799 --> 00:17:21,839
Why are you staring at me?

400
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:23,720
How was I supposed to know he's that fragile?

401
00:17:24,279 --> 00:17:24,880
You're not blaming me for this,
are you?

402
00:17:26,319 --> 00:17:27,839
Who would dare blame you, my lord?

403
00:17:28,319 --> 00:17:29,160
You're

404
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:30,640
from a noble house.

405
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:32,119
Raised in privilege your whole life.

406
00:17:32,480 --> 00:17:33,720
Of course you wouldn't understand.

407
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:35,279
A casual promise from you

408
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:36,440
is a chance most people couldn't earn

409
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:37,720
in several lifetimes.

410
00:17:38,079 --> 00:17:39,200
And

411
00:17:39,519 --> 00:17:41,119
a casual retraction from you

412
00:17:41,599 --> 00:17:42,359
is enough
to make a man cough up blood.

413
00:17:43,759 --> 00:17:44,440
Maybe

414
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:45,720
even kill him.

415
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:46,759
What are you talking about?

416
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:48,480
In fact,

417
00:17:48,759 --> 00:17:50,599
people your age

418
00:17:51,079 --> 00:17:52,160
are either working the fields,

419
00:17:52,359 --> 00:17:53,400
studying by candlelight,

420
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:54,799
or fighting at the front.

421
00:17:55,119 --> 00:17:56,200
Working their fingers to the bone

422
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:57,039
to feed their families.

423
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:59,079
But you?

424
00:17:59,279 --> 00:18:00,599
You eat, drink, and entertain yourself all day.

425
00:18:00,799 --> 00:18:01,559
Lazy and wandering.

426
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:02,960
Living off your ancestors' glory.

427
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:04,039
Producing nothing.

428
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:05,920
You contribute nothing to the country or its people.

429
00:18:06,119 --> 00:18:06,799
How dare you speak to me like that!

430
00:18:14,599 --> 00:18:15,200
Miss.
Jinzhao.

431
00:18:16,160 --> 00:18:16,759
- Stop it.
- Jinzhao.
Miss.

432
00:18:23,519 --> 00:18:24,920
This academy is a place of sages.

433
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:25,880
How dare you act so recklessly,

434
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:27,759
my lord?

435
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:29,319
You dare hurt our young lady?

436
00:18:29,480 --> 00:18:30,079
- Insolent!
- Qingpu.

437
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:33,880
Ms. Chen.

438
00:18:34,359 --> 00:18:35,000
Second Brother.

439
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:36,400
Let him go.

440
00:18:37,079 --> 00:18:38,359
He's just a madman.

441
00:18:39,039 --> 00:18:40,640
It's not worth going against him.

442
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:43,240
Enough.

443
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:45,920
Let's take care of your injury first.

444
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:01,640
Split it fifty-fifty.

445
00:20:03,480 --> 00:20:04,759
So by my math,

446
00:20:05,440 --> 00:20:06,519
we only need

447
00:20:06,519 --> 00:20:07,240
another hundred and fifty taels.

448
00:20:08,759 --> 00:20:09,599
Or

449
00:20:10,119 --> 00:20:11,079
let's make it an even two hundred.

450
00:20:11,759 --> 00:20:12,920
But here's the thing.

451
00:20:13,440 --> 00:20:15,240
You and your sister didn't grow up together.

452
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:17,160
Might feel a bit distant.

453
00:20:17,799 --> 00:20:19,200
Distance isn't a problem.

454
00:20:19,759 --> 00:20:20,559
The more distant,

455
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:22,200
the more expensive the meeting gift has to be.

456
00:20:22,440 --> 00:20:23,400
Why else would I spend five taels

457
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:25,000
on that jade bracelet?

458
00:20:25,279 --> 00:20:26,599
It's for the eldest sister.

459
00:20:27,759 --> 00:20:29,400
It's called fishing, get it?

460
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:31,799
She'll have to give something back.

461
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:33,680
Gold, jade,

462
00:20:33,680 --> 00:20:34,640
antiques or calligraphy,

463
00:20:34,960 --> 00:20:35,799
as long as it's worth more than two hundred taels,

464
00:20:36,119 --> 00:20:36,960
I win.

465
00:20:37,480 --> 00:20:39,079
The eldest miss is loaded.

466
00:20:39,599 --> 00:20:41,480
Maybe

467
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:42,839
she could even take care of that little matter

468
00:20:43,039 --> 00:20:43,759
for us without breaking a sweat.
Shut up.

469
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:45,319
Yes, sir.

470
00:20:46,359 --> 00:20:47,119
I'm an idiot.

471
00:20:47,440 --> 00:20:48,079
- That matter.
- I'm an idiot.

472
00:20:48,079 --> 00:20:49,200
Not a word of it must ever get out.

473
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:50,400
You hear me?

474
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:52,359
Understood.

475
00:20:52,759 --> 00:20:53,720
I promise I won't say a thing.

476
00:20:53,920 --> 00:20:54,960
I promise.

477
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:02,319
Not a word
about what happened today.

478
00:21:03,640 --> 00:21:04,359
Yes, miss.

479
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,680
Miss,

480
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:09,000
hurry to the main house.

481
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:10,119
Young Master Rong has returned.

482
00:21:10,319 --> 00:21:11,039
Wasn't he not coming

483
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:13,920
until the end of the month?

484
00:21:15,839 --> 00:21:16,880
Go tell the mistress

485
00:21:17,079 --> 00:21:18,640
I'll be there as soon as I change my clothes.

486
00:21:18,839 --> 00:21:19,400
Yes, miss.

487
00:21:24,519 --> 00:21:25,319
Mother.

488
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:29,240
How did you get so thin?

489
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:31,440
Your cheeks are sunken in.

490
00:21:32,319 --> 00:21:34,079
Have you been studying too hard?

491
00:21:34,319 --> 00:21:35,799
The eldest miss and the second miss are here.

492
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:38,440
I'll have to fatten you up.

493
00:21:43,480 --> 00:21:44,359
Rong.

494
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:46,079
Greetings,

495
00:21:46,519 --> 00:21:47,440
big sister.

496
00:21:48,599 --> 00:21:50,000
You've grown so tall.

497
00:21:50,359 --> 00:21:51,559
Quite the handsome young man.

498
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:52,839
Big sister, you're beautiful too.

499
00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:54,039
Like someone out of a painting.

500
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:56,759
Second sister.

501
00:21:58,000 --> 00:21:58,799
You're back.

502
00:22:00,240 --> 00:22:01,599
Everyone, please sit.

503
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:07,119
Weren't you coming back at the end of the month?

504
00:22:07,279 --> 00:22:08,400
Why the early return?

505
00:22:08,599 --> 00:22:09,599
That was the plan,

506
00:22:09,839 --> 00:22:10,720
but the teacher suddenly came down

507
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:11,799
with a bad cough,

508
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:12,920
so he let us out early.

509
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:14,599
I wrote about it

510
00:22:14,599 --> 00:22:15,759
in my letter to second sister.

511
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:17,039
Didn't she tell you?

512
00:22:19,200 --> 00:22:19,680
I thought

513
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:21,039
you wrote to Mother as well.

514
00:22:21,440 --> 00:22:22,079
So

515
00:22:22,279 --> 00:22:23,720
you only wrote to me.

516
00:22:26,160 --> 00:22:27,240
It's my fault,

517
00:22:27,240 --> 00:22:27,839
big sister.

518
00:22:28,039 --> 00:22:29,480
should have told you.

519
00:22:30,440 --> 00:22:31,079
No harm done.

520
00:22:31,359 --> 00:22:32,680
Either way,

521
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:34,240
Huaiyuan is all ready for you.

522
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:36,839
Did you bring gifts

523
00:22:36,839 --> 00:22:38,680
for your sisters?

524
00:22:38,759 --> 00:22:39,279
Yes.
Shuangli.

525
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:43,480
Big sister.

526
00:22:44,240 --> 00:22:45,079
This one is for you.

527
00:22:46,039 --> 00:22:47,119
That's thoughtful of you.

528
00:22:53,119 --> 00:22:53,839
I just picked it at random.

529
00:22:54,039 --> 00:22:55,240
The luster looked good,

530
00:22:55,359 --> 00:22:56,079
but I wasn't sure

531
00:22:56,079 --> 00:22:57,319
if it would suit you.

532
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:01,880
It's perfect.

533
00:23:02,119 --> 00:23:02,920
Thank you.

534
00:23:03,279 --> 00:23:04,119
I'm glad.

535
00:23:08,279 --> 00:23:10,359
What a beautiful ivory concentric ball.

536
00:23:11,119 --> 00:23:12,839
You actually carved it?

537
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:16,359
Did you carve this

538
00:23:16,559 --> 00:23:17,640
yourself?

539
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:18,359
Yes.

540
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:20,079
Mother, look.

541
00:23:21,319 --> 00:23:22,960
- Let me see.
- It wasn't that hard.

542
00:23:23,240 --> 00:23:24,119
No,

543
00:23:24,119 --> 00:23:25,519
but what matters is the thought behind it.

544
00:23:25,839 --> 00:23:26,440
That's worth

545
00:23:26,440 --> 00:23:27,759
more than any gold or jade.

546
00:23:28,039 --> 00:23:29,480
Last time,

547
00:23:29,680 --> 00:23:30,960
I mentioned

548
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:33,000
I wanted an ivory concentric ball.

549
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:34,240
He said he'd make me one.

550
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:35,240
I never thought

551
00:23:35,240 --> 00:23:36,480
he'd actually pull it off.

552
00:23:37,599 --> 00:23:38,240
Who would have guessed

553
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:39,480
you had such skill?

554
00:23:41,079 --> 00:23:42,160
I made another one.

555
00:23:42,359 --> 00:23:43,480
This one is for you.

556
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:45,000
But it's not finished yet.

557
00:23:45,200 --> 00:23:45,799
Once it's done,

558
00:23:45,799 --> 00:23:46,839
I'll bring it to you.

559
00:23:48,519 --> 00:23:50,440
I have a gift for you too.

560
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:51,599
Qingpu.

561
00:23:56,240 --> 00:23:57,200
Go on, open it.

562
00:24:07,079 --> 00:24:07,920
What is it?

563
00:24:13,279 --> 00:24:14,519
It's a pair of knee pads.

564
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:15,960
It's getting cold.

565
00:24:16,200 --> 00:24:17,640
You can wear them when you write.

566
00:24:18,279 --> 00:24:19,519
Your sister is so thoughtful.

567
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:21,200
She made these

568
00:24:21,200 --> 00:24:22,640
herself.

569
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:27,400
It's not gold or jade.

570
00:24:28,079 --> 00:24:29,000
Just a little something from the heart.

571
00:24:38,519 --> 00:24:39,200
Miss,

572
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,680
didn't you already give him a pair of knee pads?

573
00:24:41,359 --> 00:24:42,960
Why add this painting?

574
00:24:46,079 --> 00:24:47,440
You saw it yourself.

575
00:24:47,559 --> 00:24:48,839
The moment he saw those knee pads,

576
00:24:49,039 --> 00:24:50,400
his smile froze.

577
00:24:51,039 --> 00:24:52,440
Clearly, he didn't like them.

578
00:24:54,079 --> 00:24:55,079
So

579
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:56,440
I might as well

580
00:24:56,440 --> 00:24:57,240
give him this rooster fighting painting.

581
00:24:57,960 --> 00:24:59,519
It was meant for him anyway.

582
00:25:00,359 --> 00:25:02,000
Miss, you're so good to Mr. Ji.

583
00:25:03,279 --> 00:25:04,799
But from what I can see,

584
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:05,960
he seems closer

585
00:25:05,960 --> 00:25:08,000
to the second young lady.

586
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:10,400
They grew up together.

587
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:12,279
Of course

588
00:25:12,279 --> 00:25:13,480
he's closer to her than to me.

589
00:25:20,240 --> 00:25:21,519
You actually carved a concentric ball

590
00:25:21,680 --> 00:25:22,880
for the eldest sister?

591
00:25:23,279 --> 00:25:24,519
As if I have that much free time.

592
00:25:24,759 --> 00:25:26,000
I just said it in passing.

593
00:25:26,319 --> 00:25:27,119
It's all your fault.

594
00:25:27,480 --> 00:25:28,119
Why did you have to show off

595
00:25:28,119 --> 00:25:29,480
in front of her?

596
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:31,079
I wasn't showing off.

597
00:25:31,759 --> 00:25:33,319
I was just happy

598
00:25:33,319 --> 00:25:34,519
and said too much.

599
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:36,559
Anyway, she didn't say anything.

600
00:25:37,920 --> 00:25:39,039
Yeah.

601
00:25:39,279 --> 00:25:40,200
But all she gave me
was a lousy pair of knee pads.

602
00:25:43,920 --> 00:25:44,759
So,

603
00:25:44,759 --> 00:25:46,400
you've been sucking up to her

604
00:25:46,559 --> 00:25:47,519
because

605
00:25:47,519 --> 00:25:48,880
you're hoping for something expensive in return.

606
00:25:49,519 --> 00:25:50,720
Isn't that fair?

607
00:25:51,079 --> 00:25:52,119
I went to all that trouble

608
00:25:52,119 --> 00:25:53,160
picking out that bracelet for her.

609
00:25:54,039 --> 00:25:54,799
And
she fobs me off

610
00:25:55,519 --> 00:25:56,519
with cheap knee pads.

611
00:25:58,640 --> 00:26:00,519
Look at you, counting every penny.

612
00:26:03,400 --> 00:26:04,000
Well,
let me ask you something.

613
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:07,160
Do you have any spare money

614
00:26:07,160 --> 00:26:08,240
lately?

615
00:26:08,559 --> 00:26:09,279
No.

616
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:11,799
You haven't even heard how much.

617
00:26:12,519 --> 00:26:13,799
I don't have any.

618
00:26:14,200 --> 00:26:15,759
I only get two taels a month.

619
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:17,400
Barely enough for face powder and hair oil.

620
00:26:17,880 --> 00:26:19,279
What do you need the money for?

621
00:26:20,400 --> 00:26:21,039
I.

622
00:26:22,240 --> 00:26:23,160
Nothing.
I have my reasons.

623
00:26:24,279 --> 00:26:25,079
What reasons?

624
00:26:26,119 --> 00:26:27,200
Well, since you don't have any to lend,

625
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:27,960
don't ask.

626
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:37,079
Miss,

627
00:26:37,240 --> 00:26:39,160
why is Ms. Ji so short of money?

628
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:41,039
He even borrowed from the second young lady.

629
00:26:42,039 --> 00:26:44,079
He's still studying,

630
00:26:44,599 --> 00:26:45,640
no drinking,

631
00:26:46,000 --> 00:26:47,079
no parties.

632
00:26:47,559 --> 00:26:48,200
He shouldn't

633
00:26:48,200 --> 00:26:49,480
need that much.

634
00:26:51,799 --> 00:26:52,279
Anyway,

635
00:26:52,759 --> 00:26:54,039
none of my business.

636
00:26:57,319 --> 00:26:58,400
Miss,

637
00:26:58,599 --> 00:26:59,359
are we still giving him the painting?

638
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:00,799
Of course not.

639
00:27:01,559 --> 00:27:02,880
I'm not going to beg her.

640
00:27:04,640 --> 00:27:05,440
Besides,

641
00:27:05,920 --> 00:27:07,000
a good painting like this

642
00:27:07,279 --> 00:27:08,519
is better off with me.

643
00:27:10,160 --> 00:27:11,160
Be careful, miss.

644
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:12,680
Your arm is still hurt.

645
00:27:15,039 --> 00:27:15,599
Oh, right.

646
00:27:16,240 --> 00:27:17,359
Go get that outfit

647
00:27:17,359 --> 00:27:18,359
I was wearing.

648
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:38,279
What are you looking for?

649
00:27:43,880 --> 00:27:44,599
The notes

650
00:27:45,240 --> 00:27:46,279
I wrote in that book

651
00:27:46,279 --> 00:27:47,279
I borrowed from Mr. Chen.

652
00:27:47,559 --> 00:27:48,920
I took them out

653
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:50,559
and hid them in my sleeve.

654
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:52,440
Then Ye Xian hit me

655
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:54,599
with his whip.

656
00:27:55,000 --> 00:27:55,759
And now

657
00:27:55,960 --> 00:27:57,039
they're gone.

658
00:28:15,559 --> 00:28:17,359
[That feeling of being a guest in your own home.]

659
00:28:17,759 --> 00:28:19,160
[I know it well.]

660
00:28:19,839 --> 00:28:21,400
[Whenever it gets me down,

661
00:28:21,599 --> 00:28:22,839
I cheer myself up.]

662
00:28:23,480 --> 00:28:25,920
[Being a guest in your own home isn't all bad.]

663
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:27,839
[Since I'm the guest,

664
00:28:28,319 --> 00:28:30,119
if anyone asks to borrow money,

665
00:28:30,440 --> 00:28:31,720
absolutely not.]

666
00:28:32,599 --> 00:28:33,880
[The most important thing

667
00:28:34,279 --> 00:28:35,119
in life

668
00:28:35,720 --> 00:28:37,480
is learning to comfort yourself.]

669
00:28:38,880 --> 00:28:40,359
[Every night, tell yourself:

670
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:42,440
blame yourself less,

671
00:28:43,079 --> 00:28:44,400
find others' faults more.]

672
00:28:45,319 --> 00:28:46,480
[If that doesn't work,

673
00:28:47,039 --> 00:28:48,440
go to Linxia,

674
00:28:48,839 --> 00:28:49,759
order a feast,

675
00:28:50,400 --> 00:28:51,559
and eat.]

676
00:28:54,839 --> 00:28:55,799
[Still unhappy?]

677
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:57,319
[Eat again.]

678
00:28:57,960 --> 00:28:59,559
[Until you're stuffed

679
00:29:00,359 --> 00:29:01,559
and can't think straight.]

680
00:29:44,480 --> 00:29:45,200
In fact,

681
00:29:45,680 --> 00:29:47,400
people your age

682
00:29:47,960 --> 00:29:49,119
are either working the fields,

683
00:29:49,279 --> 00:29:50,279
studying by candlelight,

684
00:29:50,559 --> 00:29:51,839
or fighting at the front.

685
00:29:52,160 --> 00:29:53,279
Working their fingers to the bone

686
00:29:53,279 --> 00:29:54,119
to feed their families.

687
00:29:54,519 --> 00:29:55,880
But you?

688
00:29:56,079 --> 00:29:57,240
You eat, drink, and entertain yourself all day.

689
00:29:57,559 --> 00:29:58,440
Lazy and wandering.

690
00:29:59,200 --> 00:30:00,519
Living off your ancestors' glory.

691
00:30:00,519 --> 00:30:01,400
Producing nothing.

692
00:30:01,559 --> 00:30:03,440
You contribute nothing to the country or its people.

693
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:17,759
My lord,

694
00:30:17,920 --> 00:30:18,920
we should be going.

695
00:30:35,119 --> 00:30:36,039
Let him go.

696
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:38,079
He's just a madman.

697
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:40,240
It's not worth going against him.

698
00:30:53,359 --> 00:30:53,920
My lord,

699
00:30:54,279 --> 00:30:55,039
the next guests
will be here any moment.

700
00:30:56,200 --> 00:30:56,960
Linxia has already been booked

701
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:58,400
by someone else.

702
00:30:58,799 --> 00:30:59,720
Why don't you ask the young lord

703
00:30:59,720 --> 00:31:01,079
to clear the place?

704
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:02,799
Who told you to ask me to clear out?

705
00:31:03,559 --> 00:31:04,119
My lord.

706
00:31:05,680 --> 00:31:06,240
My lord.

707
00:31:06,599 --> 00:31:07,480
Yes, you.

708
00:31:07,480 --> 00:31:08,720
You want me to move?

709
00:31:09,839 --> 00:31:10,359
Get lost.
But.

710
00:31:14,799 --> 00:31:15,559
Ms. Chen.

711
00:31:15,680 --> 00:31:16,720
My respects to you.

712
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:22,519
Young lord.

713
00:31:23,400 --> 00:31:25,319
So you're the one who wants me to move?

714
00:31:27,279 --> 00:31:28,920
Where?

715
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:32,279
You think I don't want to?

716
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:34,319
You think

717
00:31:34,319 --> 00:31:36,160
I enjoy eating, drinking,

718
00:31:36,240 --> 00:31:37,440
and lazing around all day?

719
00:31:39,240 --> 00:31:40,000
Do you think

720
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:41,039
you know me so well?

721
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:42,359
Gu Jinzhao,

722
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:55,200
you don't know a damn thing.

723
00:31:55,319 --> 00:31:55,640
My lord,
let's go back.

724
00:31:56,599 --> 00:31:57,359
Get out of my way.

725
00:32:02,400 --> 00:32:03,599
You don't understand anything.

726
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:16,720
Teacher.

727
00:32:22,960 --> 00:32:24,319
How's your injury?

728
00:32:28,880 --> 00:32:30,319
I didn't mean to hurt you.

729
00:32:31,559 --> 00:32:32,319
Let me see.

730
00:32:35,920 --> 00:32:37,240
Who is that man?

731
00:32:37,839 --> 00:32:39,480
Ye Xian, heir to Marquis Changxing.

732
00:32:39,480 --> 00:32:40,319
Does it still hurt?

733
00:32:42,640 --> 00:32:44,319
Isn't that the one with the heart condition

734
00:32:44,440 --> 00:32:46,119
who can't join the army?

735
00:32:46,599 --> 00:32:48,240
Can't ride a horse,

736
00:32:48,240 --> 00:32:49,000
can't fight.

737
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:51,000
If he never earns any merit,

738
00:32:51,400 --> 00:32:53,480
he might not get the title.

739
00:32:54,440 --> 00:32:55,799
Then the Changxing line

740
00:32:56,200 --> 00:32:57,160
would die out.

741
00:32:58,319 --> 00:32:58,920
Why doesn't he

742
00:32:58,920 --> 00:33:00,000
just have more sons then?

743
00:33:00,200 --> 00:33:01,559
You think he hasn't tried?

744
00:33:01,799 --> 00:33:03,079
It's not that he won't,

745
00:33:03,720 --> 00:33:05,359
it's that he can't.

746
00:33:07,000 --> 00:33:07,799
How dare you!

747
00:33:14,119 --> 00:33:14,920
Take them back.
Yes, sir.

748
00:33:16,359 --> 00:33:16,799
My lord.

749
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:18,160
Let's go.

750
00:33:23,240 --> 00:33:23,799
Come on, my lord.
Please.

751
00:33:25,200 --> 00:33:26,039
Let's go home.

752
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:27,720
Teacher.

753
00:33:28,240 --> 00:33:28,799
This way.

754
00:33:36,880 --> 00:33:37,920
Jiuheng,

755
00:33:38,200 --> 00:33:40,000
since you manage the Eastern Palace,

756
00:33:40,559 --> 00:33:41,960
tell me,

757
00:33:42,440 --> 00:33:44,480
what do you really think of Ye Xian?

758
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:45,759
I hear

759
00:33:46,079 --> 00:33:48,359
he gets along quite well with His Highness.

760
00:33:53,279 --> 00:33:54,559
I was about to say, teacher.

761
00:33:55,759 --> 00:33:56,880
In my view,

762
00:33:57,559 --> 00:33:58,720
Ye Xian shouldn't

763
00:33:59,519 --> 00:34:01,160
stay close to His Highness.

764
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:06,640
Come on, eat.

765
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:24,119
This classmate of mine grew up poor.

766
00:34:24,679 --> 00:34:25,960
After the new year,

767
00:34:26,199 --> 00:34:27,559
his sister is getting married to some local rich man.

768
00:34:28,079 --> 00:34:28,800
He's worried her dowry
will be too shabby

769
00:34:29,800 --> 00:34:30,679
and she'll be looked down on.

770
00:34:31,079 --> 00:34:32,039
So he came to us for a loan.

771
00:34:32,519 --> 00:34:33,280
Mother never likes

772
00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:34,519
getting involved in such things.

773
00:34:34,639 --> 00:34:35,639
And Father is even worse.

774
00:34:36,519 --> 00:34:37,679
I don't have any money myself.

775
00:34:38,119 --> 00:34:38,880
So

776
00:34:38,880 --> 00:34:40,119
I had to come to you.

777
00:34:40,719 --> 00:34:41,800
How much do you need?

778
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:42,960
Two hundred taels.

779
00:34:43,480 --> 00:34:44,320
That much?

780
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:47,239
That's not a small sum.

781
00:34:47,960 --> 00:34:49,119
Give me a few days.

782
00:34:49,119 --> 00:34:50,280
Let me see what I can scrape together.

783
00:34:50,599 --> 00:34:51,079
All right?

784
00:34:53,320 --> 00:34:53,840
I.

785
00:35:00,199 --> 00:35:00,760
Well.

786
00:35:01,599 --> 00:35:02,440
Alright then.

787
00:35:03,239 --> 00:35:04,079
I'll be going now.

788
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:18,320
Miss,

789
00:35:19,199 --> 00:35:20,880
Yunting from Mr. Chen's side is here.

790
00:35:21,199 --> 00:35:22,280
He said

791
00:35:22,280 --> 00:35:23,519
the seventeenth is Mr. Chen's birthday,

792
00:35:23,639 --> 00:35:25,079
and he'd like to invite you.

793
00:35:25,679 --> 00:35:27,519
He also wants to know

794
00:35:27,519 --> 00:35:28,199
how your injury is doing.
Really?

795
00:35:29,920 --> 00:35:31,079
He actually said

796
00:35:31,079 --> 00:35:32,559
the seventeenth is his birthday?

797
00:35:37,000 --> 00:35:38,599
But that day at the academy,

798
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:40,039
he was right there,

799
00:35:40,920 --> 00:35:42,480
yet he sent someone else to see me.

800
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:44,159
Now he's inviting me himself.

801
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:46,360
I don't know what to make of it.

802
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:48,920
Maybe last time,

803
00:35:48,920 --> 00:35:50,480
he couldn't come out

804
00:35:50,840 --> 00:35:52,199
to see you alone

805
00:35:52,199 --> 00:35:53,320
because your brother was around.

806
00:35:54,239 --> 00:35:55,199
I think so too.

807
00:35:56,159 --> 00:35:57,880
Then have Yunting ask him.

808
00:35:58,119 --> 00:35:59,440
We'll meet

809
00:35:59,719 --> 00:36:00,679
on Yong'an Bridge.

810
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:01,360
okay?

811
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:02,920
I'll go ask him.

812
00:36:06,320 --> 00:36:07,320
My lady wants to meet

813
00:36:07,480 --> 00:36:08,320
on Yong'an Bridge

814
00:36:08,320 --> 00:36:09,440
on the seventeenth.

815
00:36:11,960 --> 00:36:12,519
Got it.

816
00:36:25,480 --> 00:36:27,000
Young Master Rong is here.

817
00:36:38,239 --> 00:36:39,800
How are you managing this room?

818
00:36:39,960 --> 00:36:41,039
Not even a cup of water.

819
00:36:49,760 --> 00:36:50,599
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

820
00:36:58,519 --> 00:36:59,639
Idiot! Idiot!

821
00:37:00,039 --> 00:37:01,280
Are you trying to burn me alive?

822
00:37:01,360 --> 00:37:02,000
Forgive me, my lord.

823
00:37:13,159 --> 00:37:13,960
Hot?

824
00:37:14,119 --> 00:37:15,480
Then let it cool down.

825
00:37:16,239 --> 00:37:17,199
What's the rush?

826
00:37:17,559 --> 00:37:18,559
Who put you in a bad mood?

827
00:37:18,559 --> 00:37:19,719
You come here to take it out on me.

828
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:22,000
Don't ask.

829
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:25,320
Let me guess.

830
00:37:25,920 --> 00:37:27,000
Father's not home.

831
00:37:27,199 --> 00:37:28,320
Mother spoils you too much

832
00:37:28,320 --> 00:37:29,639
to let you suffer.

833
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:32,320
So,

834
00:37:32,599 --> 00:37:33,559
it must be eldest sister?

835
00:37:36,159 --> 00:37:37,079
Bingo.

836
00:37:37,599 --> 00:37:38,280
No wonder.

837
00:37:38,440 --> 00:37:39,360
Actually,
no one dares cross her.

838
00:37:40,800 --> 00:37:41,760
She doesn't even put Father

839
00:37:41,760 --> 00:37:42,880
in his place.

840
00:37:43,079 --> 00:37:44,400
You'd better stop provoking her.

841
00:37:46,760 --> 00:37:47,440
Why should I?

842
00:37:47,960 --> 00:37:49,039
She's the eldest miss, sure,

843
00:37:49,039 --> 00:37:50,280
but I'm the eldest young master of the Gu family.

844
00:37:51,920 --> 00:37:53,119
What happened?

845
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:54,760
Tell me.

846
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:57,719
Why bring up something so shameful?

847
00:37:59,559 --> 00:38:00,440
Miss! Miss!

848
00:38:03,679 --> 00:38:04,840
Young Master Rong.

849
00:38:05,440 --> 00:38:06,519
What...

850
00:38:08,239 --> 00:38:09,360
Where have you been all morning?

851
00:38:09,639 --> 00:38:10,559
Not a proper person
in the room.

852
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:12,679
And because of that,
our young master burned his mouth on tea.

853
00:38:13,639 --> 00:38:14,880
Now he's throwing a tantrum at me.

854
00:38:15,559 --> 00:38:16,199
Miss.

855
00:38:21,320 --> 00:38:22,199
What's going on?

856
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:23,480
Why so secretive?

857
00:38:31,360 --> 00:38:32,280
Did you hear clearly?

858
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:33,679
Every word.

859
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:39,639
I just heard something

860
00:38:40,039 --> 00:38:41,119
about eldest sister.

861
00:38:41,559 --> 00:38:43,039
I'm not interested in her business.

862
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:45,000
Not interested at all?

863
00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:46,639
This person
might just become

864
00:38:47,360 --> 00:38:48,519
our brother-in-law someday.

865
00:38:49,519 --> 00:38:50,159
What?

866
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:52,239
Brother-in-law?

867
00:38:53,400 --> 00:38:53,960
Who?

868
00:38:55,679 --> 00:38:57,079
Chen Xuanqing.

869
00:39:04,199 --> 00:39:05,199
On Yong'an Bridge.

870
00:39:07,519 --> 00:39:09,239
That new bridge

871
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:11,039
I haven't seen it yet.

872
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:12,480
Great.
Alright then.

873
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:14,559
I'll go give Miss Qingpu an answer
in a bit.

874
00:39:15,800 --> 00:39:17,000
Miss Qingpu said

875
00:39:17,199 --> 00:39:18,239
Miss Gu is already thinking about

876
00:39:18,239 --> 00:39:19,679
what birthday gift to get you.

877
00:39:20,760 --> 00:39:21,519
You told her
my birthday?

878
00:39:22,599 --> 00:39:23,079
Yes.

879
00:39:23,440 --> 00:39:25,199
You're meeting Miss Gu on the seventeenth.

880
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:26,880
Isn't that because

881
00:39:27,199 --> 00:39:28,119
you want to spend your birthday with her?

882
00:39:28,320 --> 00:39:28,920
I picked the seventeenth

883
00:39:28,920 --> 00:39:30,400
because the academy is closed that day.

884
00:39:30,559 --> 00:39:31,079
You.

885
00:39:32,559 --> 00:39:33,159
Anyway,

886
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:34,800
it's already said.

887
00:39:35,280 --> 00:39:36,320
I think

888
00:39:36,440 --> 00:39:37,639
Miss Gu is quite nice.

889
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:38,679
Pretty,

890
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:39,760
wealthy,

891
00:39:40,079 --> 00:39:41,400
and generous.

892
00:39:41,960 --> 00:39:43,480
Way better

893
00:39:43,599 --> 00:39:44,679
than those noble ladies.

894
00:39:46,239 --> 00:39:46,800
Enough.

895
00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:48,760
That's a young lady.

896
00:39:49,239 --> 00:39:50,360
Don't gossip about her like that behind her back.

897
00:39:51,480 --> 00:39:52,119
I'll head back now.
Wait.

898
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:53,400
Wait,

899
00:39:53,840 --> 00:39:54,559
you forgot.

900
00:39:54,880 --> 00:39:55,639
Today the old lady

901
00:39:55,639 --> 00:39:56,840
asked you to come home.

902
00:39:58,800 --> 00:39:59,159
Right.
I forgot.

903
00:40:00,239 --> 00:40:00,599
Let's go.

904
00:40:05,199 --> 00:40:07,119
Ever since you became a Top Scholar,

905
00:40:07,599 --> 00:40:09,079
people have been lining up

906
00:40:09,079 --> 00:40:10,559
to propose.

907
00:40:11,039 --> 00:40:12,280
I know

908
00:40:12,639 --> 00:40:13,760
many well-bred young ladies

909
00:40:14,039 --> 00:40:16,199
in the capital

910
00:40:17,079 --> 00:40:18,920
have their eye on you.

911
00:40:20,079 --> 00:40:20,840
Grandmother.

912
00:40:21,880 --> 00:40:22,679
I.

913
00:40:22,679 --> 00:40:24,280
Never mind.

914
00:40:25,039 --> 00:40:26,079
What do you think of

915
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:29,000
Yu Wanxue?

916
00:40:30,280 --> 00:40:32,760
The Yu family may not be as high ranked as ours,

917
00:40:33,480 --> 00:40:35,719
but they've been scholars for generations.

918
00:40:36,960 --> 00:40:38,360
Your uncle Yu

919
00:40:38,639 --> 00:40:40,519
is a man of pure character.

920
00:40:41,599 --> 00:40:42,960
He and your third uncle

921
00:40:43,159 --> 00:40:45,239
have been close friends for years.

922
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:47,440
We know each other well.

923
00:40:47,920 --> 00:40:48,880
And

924
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:50,599
Wanxue

925
00:40:51,079 --> 00:40:53,679
is a rare, fine young lady.

926
00:40:54,400 --> 00:40:55,519
What do you say?

927
00:40:57,079 --> 00:40:58,199
Well,

928
00:40:58,519 --> 00:40:59,800
what does third uncle think?

929
00:41:00,360 --> 00:41:02,519
He's the one who picked her.

930
00:41:03,599 --> 00:41:05,079
And I agree.

931
00:41:05,960 --> 00:41:07,800
It does seem like a good match.

932
00:41:08,480 --> 00:41:10,320
As for the Yu family,

933
00:41:10,760 --> 00:41:12,400
they want to wait until after the new year

934
00:41:12,599 --> 00:41:14,199
to exchange the birth certificates.

935
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:15,880
But of course,

936
00:41:17,639 --> 00:41:20,320
you have to have your say.

937
00:41:20,679 --> 00:41:22,920
It's your marriage.

938
00:41:34,920 --> 00:41:35,480
My lord,

939
00:41:35,800 --> 00:41:36,840
you're finally awake.

940
00:41:39,639 --> 00:41:40,800
What time is it?

941
00:41:40,960 --> 00:41:41,880
Just past nine in the morning.

942
00:41:42,199 --> 00:41:43,440
You drank too much yesterday.

943
00:41:43,599 --> 00:41:43,960
You slept

944
00:41:43,960 --> 00:41:45,119
a full fourteen hours.

945
00:41:50,920 --> 00:41:52,400
What about Gu Jinzhao?

946
00:41:53,679 --> 00:41:54,400
Greetings, my lady.

947
00:41:54,679 --> 00:41:55,440
Xian,

948
00:41:56,119 --> 00:41:57,280
you just woke up?

949
00:41:59,199 --> 00:41:59,920
Someone come.

950
00:42:00,199 --> 00:42:01,639
Help him wash up.

951
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:03,559
And pack a few changes of clothes.

952
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:04,360
Yes.

953
00:42:05,039 --> 00:42:05,519
Xian,
I've already sent word

954
00:42:06,360 --> 00:42:07,440
to your sister.

955
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:08,719
You'll go over there in a bit

956
00:42:09,039 --> 00:42:10,400
and stay at Daxin for a few days.

957
00:42:12,559 --> 00:42:13,480
What happened?

958
00:42:13,760 --> 00:42:15,239
Your father just returned from court.

959
00:42:15,480 --> 00:42:16,079
His Majesty dismissed you

960
00:42:16,079 --> 00:42:17,719
from your post as the Crown Prince's companion.

961
00:42:17,960 --> 00:42:18,400
What?
This.

962
00:42:20,039 --> 00:42:21,000
Did you ask Father

963
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:22,119
to beg His Majesty?

964
00:42:22,320 --> 00:42:24,079
No, of course not.

965
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:26,079
I did think about it before,

966
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:27,440
but you didn't want it.

967
00:42:27,760 --> 00:42:28,880
Your father also said

968
00:42:29,119 --> 00:42:30,079
it was a good path.

969
00:42:30,079 --> 00:42:31,199
So

970
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:32,559
I dropped it.

971
00:42:33,159 --> 00:42:34,039
But

972
00:42:34,320 --> 00:42:35,039
who would have guessed that

973
00:42:35,039 --> 00:42:36,400
today His Majesty suddenly told your father that

974
00:42:36,719 --> 00:42:38,119
since you have a heart condition,

975
00:42:38,360 --> 00:42:39,800
you should stay home and rest.

976
00:42:40,039 --> 00:42:41,280
He also said some other things.

977
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:43,039
Anyway,

978
00:42:43,639 --> 00:42:45,320
right in front of all the civil and military officials,

979
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:46,800
he embarrassed your father badly.

980
00:42:47,079 --> 00:42:47,960
Luckily,

981
00:42:48,159 --> 00:42:49,400
the Earl of Yongchang came to discuss something with him.

982
00:42:49,519 --> 00:42:50,239
You need to leave

983
00:42:50,559 --> 00:42:51,679
before he comes to his senses

984
00:42:51,880 --> 00:42:52,920
and starts yelling at you again.

985
00:43:07,679 --> 00:43:08,360
My lord.

986
00:43:09,239 --> 00:43:09,760
Chen Yi.

987
00:43:13,639 --> 00:43:14,559
Young lord.
